data.description: Rare find! Come see this 3 bedroom 2 bath pool home located on a cleared double lot. Home features include screened in patio with large in ground pool. Huge kitchen newly remodeled in 2022 with 17 cabinets and 10 drawers, large island with granite counter-tops along with open shelving. Kitchen includes farmhouse sink and all stainless steel appliances with a propane cook top and double built in oven perfect for family gatherings. Brand new HVAC system in 2016, new roof 2018, and new hot water heater in 2022. Large open concept included in remodel with all new vinyl plank flooring and freshly painted interior. This home won't last long, schedule your showing now! *Chandelier does not convey. *Seller is licensed real estate agent. Sale price includes the cleared .243 acre lot directly behind the home, tax number 07-11-31-7026-0023-0140 (31 Pine Cedar Dr) which is a totally build-able lot.
